extendedInfo.description: Tera FansApp - the perfect application describing the online MMO game! Main feature: - Characters view!!! Don't miss it! - Server status (auto-refresh every minute)! This application provides a description of the sections:  - Races descriptions (common information, details, history) - Classes descriptions (common information, details, skill of classes) - Interactive worldmap - Achievements of the game - Guides information (beginners, camprife, transport, the nexus) - Gameplay information (the basics, groups, guilds, pvp, dungeons, endgame) - Equipment (armor, stuffs, customizing, crafting, craft theory)  - Server status (Europe && USA servers)- Items description (accessory, crystals, weapons, armor)- Media (screenshots, video and wallpapers)
